chapter:
  Create new scope


Scope class is a special extension class annotated with @Scope qualifier. Scope class
    should implements or extends a class that implements com.vaadin.ui.Component.


Scope extension point is com.peergreen.webconsole.scope

@Extension
@ExtensionPoint("com.peergreen.webconsole.scope")
@Scope("home")
public class HomeScope extends VerticalLayout {
  // home scope body
}


See @Scope section for more details
